) write SQL queries using Aggregate operators (MIN, MAX, SUM, COUNT, AVG) for the following schema
Sailors (sid, sname, age, rating)
i) find the average age of sailors
ii) find the minimum age of sailors
iii) find the maximum age of sailors
iv) find the number of sailors
v) find the total rating of all sailors
vi) Write about DCL commands

i)Find the average age of sailors
SELECT AVG(age) AS average_age FROM Sailors;

ii) Find the minimum age of sailors
SELECT MIN(age) AS minimum_age FROM Sailors;

iii) Find the maximum age of sailors
SELECT MAX(age) AS maximum_age FROM Sailors;

iv) Find the number of sailors
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_sailors FROM Sailors;

v) Find the total rating of all sailors
SELECT SUM(rating) AS total_rating FROM Sailors;

vi)
GRANT SELECT, INSERT ON Sailors TO user1;
REVOKE INSERT ON Sailors FROM user1;




